---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout 
  title="Cybersecurity Compliance Checklist for Small Business 2026 | Free Audit Tool"
  description="Free cybersecurity compliance checklist for small businesses. Complete 10-point audit for insurance and GDPR requirements. Buy once, use forever - no monthly fees."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Cybersecurity Compliance Checklist for Small Business 2026</h1>

    <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
      <strong>Need to get your insurance broker off your back?</strong> Complete this 10-point cybersecurity compliance checklist to identify exactly what you need for audit and insurance requirements.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 mt-8">Why This Checklist Works</h2>

    <p class="mb-4"><strong>Business owners think:</strong> "I just need to get this insurance broker off my back."</p>
    
    <p class="mb-4"><strong>Product pages say:</strong> "Here is stuff you can buy." → Response: Maybe later.</p>
    
    <p class="mb-6"><strong>This checklist says:</strong> "Here are the 10 gaps in your business right now." → Response: Oh no, I need to fix these.</p>

    <hr class="my-8">

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Small Business Cybersecurity Compliance Checklist</h2>

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 mt-6">Section 1: Documentation Requirements</h3>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
      <table class="min-w-full border border-gray-300">
        <thead class="bg-gray-100">
          <tr>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">#</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Requirement for Insurance/Audit</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Status</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">How to Fix It</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">1</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>Documented Password Policy</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">[ ]</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">YES - Included in Basic/Pro Kit</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">2</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>Acceptable Use Policy</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">[ ]</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">YES - Included in Basic/Pro Kit</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">3</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>Data Retention Policy</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">[ ]</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">YES - Included in Basic/Pro Kit</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">4</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>Remote Work & BYOD Policy</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">[ ]</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">YES - Included in Basic/Pro Kit</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-8">

    <p class="text-sm italic"><em>Bookmark this page - you'll need it for your next insurance renewal or audit!</em></p>
  </section>
</Layout>
